f=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gqg1665702836640.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gqg1665702836640.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gqg1665702836640.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gqg1665702836640\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Define Field List\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"gqg1665702836640__define_field_list_34532\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the fields that Uniface manages at run time for the current component entity.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gqg1665702836640__p_d9881e1_d9882e1_d9883e1\">The default field list type is Automatic, meaning that\n         Uniface manages only the fields referenced in the component. For more information, see\n            <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swv1705469594262.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swv1705469594262.html\" title=\"A component's field list determines how Uniface manages the fields when retrieving occurrences into the component at runtime. The field list includes not only the fields that are part of the component data structure, but also other fields that may be required, for example, because they are referenced in ProcScript or part of a key.\">Field Lists</a>. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gqg1665702836640__topic_d7977e1_d7978e1_d7979e1_d7980e1_d7981e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d353452e63\">\n                       \n Fields\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gqg1665702836640__li_d4520e1_d4521e1_d4522e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jmg1665702703110.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jmg1665702703110.html\" title=\"Specifies the component entity fields that Uniface manages at runtime. Valid values are Automatic (default), All Fields, and User-defined.\">Field List</a>—specified how the field list is determined. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Automatic</code> (default), <code class=\"ph codeph\">All Fields</code>, and <code class=\"ph codeph\">User-defined</code>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gqg1665702836640__li_d4523e1_d4524e1_d4525e1\">Fields—lists the fields of the modeled entity from which this component entity is derived.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gqg1665702836640__topic_d7982e1_d7983e1_d7984e1_d7985e1_d7986e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d353452e103\">\n                       \n How to\n </h2>\n<ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gqg1665702836640__li_d4526e1_d4527e1_d4528e1\">Set the value of the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field List</span> property.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gqg1665702836640__li_d4529e1_d4530e1_d4531e1\">If you choose, <code class=\"ph codeph\">User-defined</code>, a checkbox is displayed in front of each field, enabling you to select the fields you want to have. Uniface manage, in addition to those that are included automatically.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gqg1665702836640__li_d4532e1_d4533e1_d4534e1\">Click OK to save your selection.\n </li>\n</ol>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527968\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527968\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Field List Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Field List Specify the fields that Uniface manages at run time for the current component entity. The default field list type is Automatic, meaning that Uniface manages only the fields referenced in the component. For more information, see Field Lists . Fields Field List —specified how the field list is determined. Valid values are Automatic (default), All Fields , and User-defined . Fields—lists the fields of the modeled entity from which this component entity is derived. How to Set the value of the Field List property. If you choose, User-defined , a checkbox is displayed in front of each field, enabling you to select the fields you want to have. Uniface manage, in addition to those that are included automatically. Click OK to save your selection. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}